      </div>
      <div class="intro-text col-md">
        This project will create a page on an imaginary publishing company’s website to display a sample chapter from a book. The page will be designed as a ‘liquid layout’, so its columns will squash and stretch as the browser window is resized. It has a simple format with a title bar above some site links, followed by content that’s split between two columns: a column on the left containing book-related links plus a mailing list form, and a column on the right containing the sample chapter...
